%% Diagram: Chaos engineering at Netflix — from Chaos Monkey to a continuous experimentation pipeline
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    A["2010–2011\nChaos Monkey\nrandom instance kill\nin business hours"]
    B["Jul 2011\nSimian Army\nLatency / Conformity /\nDoctor / Janitor / Security"]
    C["2012–2014\nChaos Gorilla (AZ)\nChaos Kong (Region)"]
    D["Oct 2014\nFIT — Failure Injection\nrequest-level via Zuul"]
    E["Sep 2015\nPrinciples of Chaos\n(Basiri, Hochstein, Rosenthal)"]
    F["Jul 2017\nChAP — Chaos\nAutomation Platform\ncanary-style experiments"]
    G["2020s\ncontinuous resilience\nexperiments on prod traffic"]

    A --> B --> C --> D --> E --> F --> G
